  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2008-06-09",
    "date": "2008-07-09T14:33:45Z",
    "text": "Home Office Deduction Simplification Act of 2008 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a taxpayer who uses a residence to conduct a trade or business a standard tax deduction equal to the lesser of $1,500 or the taxpayer's gross trade or business income derived from the business use of such residence."
